3.00	Nirmalendu_Goon	Nirmalendu Goon	Nirmalendu Goon (Bengali: ) (born 1945) is a Bangladeshi poet, and one of the most popular poets in Bangladesh, lauded by many for his accessible verse in an age where Bangla poetry has become increasingly complex.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/96/Nirmalendu_Goon%2C_2006.jpg/200px-Nirmalendu_Goon%2C_2006.jpg
